WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.524 --> 00:00:03.142
- Hi, I'm Sal Kahn, founder
of the Kahn Academy.

00:00:03.142 --> 00:00:04.902
I'm here to invite you to participate in

00:00:04.902 --> 00:00:08.538
an exciting project that
we have around career.

00:00:08.538 --> 00:00:10.772
Our mission statement,
as a not for profit,

00:00:10.772 --> 00:00:12.522
is to provide a free world-class education

00:00:12.522 --> 00:00:14.538
for anyone anywhere.

00:00:14.538 --> 00:00:17.629
Part of that is help people
navigate their careers.

00:00:17.629 --> 00:00:19.036
What do they want to major in?

00:00:19.036 --> 00:00:20.347
What jobs do they want to pursue?

00:00:20.347 --> 00:00:22.568
What are the implications on their life

00:00:22.568 --> 00:00:24.429
in terms of finance?

00:00:24.429 --> 00:00:26.149
This is part of a
partnership that we're doing

00:00:26.149 --> 00:00:27.485
with Bank of America.

00:00:27.485 --> 00:00:29.690
We're looking for people
in all walks of life,

00:00:29.690 --> 00:00:32.068
in all sorts of careers, who are willing

00:00:32.068 --> 00:00:34.660
to be videotaped and
answer questions about

00:00:34.660 --> 00:00:36.125
how they chose their careers,

00:00:36.125 --> 00:00:39.540
the good, the bad, money questions,

00:00:39.540 --> 00:00:41.443
how they budget, how much they make.

00:00:41.443 --> 00:00:42.836
- Hi, my name is Tamillia James,

00:00:42.836 --> 00:00:44.648
and I'm a high school guidance counselor.

00:00:44.648 --> 00:00:45.481
- My name's Eddie.

00:00:45.481 --> 00:00:47.433
I'm 26 years old, and I
work as a health coach.

00:00:47.433 --> 00:00:48.704
- My name is Emmie Kelsey.

00:00:48.704 --> 00:00:49.742
I'm 22 years old.

00:00:49.742 --> 00:00:51.761
I work as a business associate

00:00:51.761 --> 00:00:53.624
at an indoor vertical farming startup.

00:00:53.624 --> 00:00:54.743
- My name's Anna Nelson.

00:00:54.743 --> 00:00:56.338
I'm 28 years old.

00:00:56.338 --> 00:00:58.468
I'm an instructional
designer at a startup.

00:00:58.468 --> 00:01:01.039
- A health coach is a
number of different things,

00:01:01.039 --> 00:01:04.291
depending on the individual
that we come across.

00:01:04.291 --> 00:01:07.236
It can be a motivational interviewer.

00:01:07.236 --> 00:01:09.049
It can be an exercise partner.

00:01:09.049 --> 00:01:10.397
- We're not like a traditional company

00:01:10.397 --> 00:01:12.373
where I have an immediate supervisor

00:01:12.373 --> 00:01:14.168
that I get all of my work from.

00:01:14.168 --> 00:01:16.446
- Currently I make $90,000 a year.

00:01:16.446 --> 00:01:18.929
- When I first started as a
high school guidance counselor

00:01:18.929 --> 00:01:20.802
and I was making $50,000.

00:01:20.802 --> 00:01:24.264
- When I finally left graduate school,

00:01:24.264 --> 00:01:26.889
I had something like $72,000 in debt.

00:01:26.889 --> 00:01:28.312
- If you're interested in participating,

00:01:28.312 --> 00:01:30.894
you'd like to be on
camera, answering questions

00:01:30.894 --> 00:01:33.119
about where you are in your career,

00:01:33.119 --> 00:01:36.215
questions about finance,
decisions that you've made,

00:01:36.215 --> 00:01:38.420
please click on the link below

00:01:38.420 --> 00:01:40.308
and submit either a short video,

00:01:40.308 --> 00:01:44.061
or a short written piece
about what you do and why.

00:01:44.061 --> 00:01:47.144
(light upbeat music)

